{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fb249e70a9","title":"夺取平介灵霜巩固孝义","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4c013c37a7","index":0,"year":1947,"month":1,"day":18,"articleId":"fb249e70a9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"eeadf606aa","type":"paragraph","text":"夺取平介灵霜巩固孝义口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"fb249e70a9"},{"id":"248570273e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年1月18日）陈、谢，王、彭，并告贺、李”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"fb249e70a9"},{"id":"0cf082f36c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）攻克孝义甚惠。（二）如平、介之政向你们攻击，你们可于野战中并灭之而后夺取平、介，如平、介之敌不动，你们即应攻击介休，调动平遥及灵、霍巴之敌增援而歼灭之，然后逐一夺取平遥、灵、霍，如此则孝义可巩固。如你们不打平、介、灵、霍而打汾阳，则孝义必失守。你们打汾阳，应在平、介、灵、霍大胜之后","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"fb249e70a9"},{"id":"697047ac55","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"fb249e70a9"},{"id":"9c84148a03","type":"paragraph","text":"子巧[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给晋莫普豫野战军第四纵队司令员陈质、政治委员谢富治和晋缓野战军第二纵队司令员王震、副司令员彭绍解的电报。2]贺、李，指贺龙、李井泉，当时分别任晋绥军区司令员和政治委员。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"fb249e70a9"}],"page":{"id":"80a4bdb23e","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"fb249e70a9","start":372,"end":372}}}},"__N_SSG":true}